text: Sathanur is a village located near Yelahanka in Bangalore of Karnataka, India. ==Transport== Sathanur is located at 9 km from Yelahanka . ===Bus=== Bus routes 401BK, 289Z, 289L, 289P, 289M serve Sathanur ===Rail=== Yelahanka Jn. is the nearest railway station ==References== Category:Villages in Bangalore Urban district
title: Sathanur, Bangalore
